### 4. DATA FETCHING HOOKS

**Pattern:** No React Query - manual fetch + useState + useCallback + useEffect

**Files:**
- `/Users/marcus/conductor/workspaces/brain-v1/lahore-v1/app/src/client/hooks/use-learnings.ts`
- `/Users/marcus/conductor/workspaces/brain-v1/lahore-v1/app/src/client/hooks/use-policies.ts`
