 10→ *   - POST /api/workspaces/:workspaceId/tools/:toolId/grants (can_use edges)
 11→ *   - POST /api/workspaces/:workspaceId/providers (credential provider CRUD)
 12→ *   - POST /api/workspaces/:workspaceId/accounts/connect/:providerId (account connection)
 13→ *   - DELETE /api/workspaces/:workspaceId/accounts/:accountId (account revocation)
 14→ *   - GET /api/workspaces/:workspaceId/identities/:identityId/toolset (effective toolset)
 15→ *   - POST /proxy/llm/anthropic/v1/messages (proxy with tool injection + interception)
 16→ */
