## 11. API CALL PATTERN

**Standard Pattern:**
1. Get workspaceId from workspace state
2. Build full URL: `/api/workspaces/${workspaceId}/<domain>/<resource>`
3. `fetch()` with method (GET/POST/PUT)
4. Handle 200 success and non-200 errors
5. Parse JSON response
6. Update local state
7. Return success boolean or result data

**Error Handling:**
